parcel.description: Legendary was Xanadu where Kubla Khan decreed his stately pleasure dome. Today, almost as legendary is  BROOKHAVEN, CryptoVoxels largest private pleasure ground. Here, in Origin City, a private dwelling was commissioned and successfully built. One hundred thousand trees, twenty thousand tons of marble are the ingredients of BROOKHAVENs structure. Contents of BROOKHAVENs palace: paintings, pictures, statues, the very stones of many another palace  a collection of everything so big it can never be catalogued or appraised, enough for ten museums  the loot of the world. Like the pharaohs, BROOKHAVENs landlord will leave many stones to mark his grave. Since the pyramids, BROOKHAVEN is the costliest monument a man has built to himself. Brookhavens landlord, a potent figure in the MetaVerse,  CryptoVoxels own Kubla Khan, BROOKHAWK.
